{
  "script_id": "even-odd",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "even-odd",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/even-odd/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.53,
      "size": 40464,
      "text": "我们每天都在和数字打交道，可你注意过吗，数字其实分成两大家族。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "even-odd",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/even-odd/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32256,
      "text": "一个叫偶数，一个叫奇数。它们藏着许多有趣的规律。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "even-odd",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/even-odd/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.87,
      "size": 29952,
      "text": "今天，我们就把数字排成方格，一眼看清这些规律。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "even-odd",
      "section_id": "parity",
      "line_id": "parity-1",
      "filename": "parity-parity-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/even-odd/xiaoxiao/parity-parity-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.11,
      "size": 33696,
      "text": "能被二整除的数，就是偶数，比如二、四、六、八。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "even-odd",
      "section_id": "parity",
      "line_id": "parity-2",
      "filename": "parity-parity-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/even-odd/xiaoxiao/parity-parity-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.18,
      "size": 34848,
      "text": "不能被二整除的数，就是奇数，比如一、三、五、七。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "even-odd",
      "section_id": "parity",
      "line_id": "parity-3",
      "filename": "parity-parity-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/even-odd/xiaoxiao/parity-parity-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.93,
      "size": 30816,
      "text": "看方格里，偶数被点亮，一个隔一个，整整齐齐。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "even-odd",
      "section_id": "rules",
      "line_id": "rules-1",
      "filename": "rules-rules-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/even-odd/xiaoxiao/rules-rules-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.58,
      "size": 41328,
      "text": "奇偶数相加也有规律：偶数加偶数还是偶数，奇数加奇数也是偶数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "even-odd",
      "section_id": "rules",
      "line_id": "rules-2",
      "filename": "rules-rules-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/even-odd/xiaoxiao/rules-rules-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.72,
      "size": 27504,
      "text": "可是一个奇数加一个偶数，结果就变成了奇数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "even-odd",
      "section_id": "rules",
      "line_id": "rules-3",
      "filename": "rules-rules-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/even-odd/xiaoxiao/rules-rules-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.55,
      "size": 40752,
      "text": "相乘时，只要有一个偶数，积就是偶数；两个都是奇数，积才是奇数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "even-odd",
      "section_id": "divide",
      "line_id": "divide-1",
      "filename": "divide-divide-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/even-odd/xiaoxiao/divide-divide-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.18,
      "size": 34848,
      "text": "如果一个数除以另一个数，余数是零，我们就说它能被整除。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "even-odd",
      "section_id": "divide",
      "line_id": "divide-2",
      "filename": "divide-divide-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/even-odd/xiaoxiao/divide-divide-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33840,
      "text": "换成除以三来点亮，你会看到三的倍数，每隔两个出现一次。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "even-odd",
      "section_id": "divide",
      "line_id": "divide-3",
      "filename": "divide-divide-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/even-odd/xiaoxiao/divide-divide-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.2,
      "size": 35136,
      "text": "除以五时，点亮的都是个位是零或五的数，规律一目了然。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "even-odd",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/even-odd/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.92,
      "size": 30672,
      "text": "切换不同的除数，看看方格上点亮的花纹怎么变化。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "even-odd",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/even-odd/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.01,
      "size": 32112,
      "text": "数一数每种除数点亮了多少个，试着找出其中的规律。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "even-odd",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/even-odd/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.3,
      "size": 36864,
      "text": "偶数能被二整除，奇数不能，它们的加法和乘法都有固定规律。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "even-odd",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/even-odd/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.03,
      "size": 32544,
      "text": "整除就是余数为零，被整除的数正是那个除数的倍数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "even-odd",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/even-odd/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.14,
      "size": 34272,
      "text": "把数字排成格子，规律就藏在花纹里。我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 36.38999999999999,
  "total_size": 581904
}